<author>ʿmạd ʿạdl, sạmḥ rwbyl</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- (mʿ sẖrwq ạlsẖms .. mʿ lḥn ạlṭywr
 fy lwn ạlzhwr .. ạ̉sẖwf jmạl yswʿ)2
 ạlqrạr- (ạ̉sẖwfk yạ yswʿ .. ạ̉sẖwfk bạlạ̹ymạn
 wạtẖq fyk msrwr .. ḥạss bạlạ̉mạn)2
 2- (mʿ gẖrwb ạlsẖms .. fy wqt ạlẓlạm
 lmạ ạlkwn ynạm .. ạ̉lms slạm yswʿ)2
 3- (lmạ ạ̉kwn frḥạn .. ạ̉htf bạllsạn
 ḥty̱ wạnạ zʿlạn .. ạ̉lms ḥnạn yswʿ)2</lyrics>
<title>mʿ sẖrwq ạlsẖms</title>
</song>